text:
Oh...
The cherry blossoms are in bloom...

Let's slow down a bit
and take our time to look.

...Huh?
Did we change the course by any chance...?

Yes
I wanted to show you these cherry blossoms here.

The beauty of the scenery
is the essence of outdoor running, after all!

All right, since I know a good spot
shall I guide you?

Oh,
I'd appreciate that, please do!
